                          <li>25th Dec - 31st Dec 2013 - Cheshire Oaks, Portsmouth, Inverness, Truro, Manchester Trafford Centre, Milton Keynes Midsummer Arcade, Derby Westfield Centre</li>
                        </ul>
                      </li>
                      <li>We encourage you to make a note of the expiry date of your token codes.</li>
                      <li>Only PizzaExpress token codes can be used in PizzaExpress restaurants, no other token codes will be accepted.</li>
                      <li>PizzaExpress token codes can be used as full or part payment for food only (PizzaExpress token codes cannot be used to purchase drinks, merchandise, gift cards or towards promotional and set menus) but you can top them up with cash; no change is given from PizzaExpress token codes and they cannot be used for a tip.</li>
                      <li>Maximum of 8 guests per party.</li>
                      <li>Token codes are not transferable.</li>
                      <li>Clubcard vouchers are not accepted by suppliers; you must exchange them for PizzaExpress token codes.</li>
                      <li>Token codes are valid for 6 months after issue.</li>
                      <li>It is not possible to combine tokens delivered via email and via post at PizzaExpress at the same time.</li>
                      <li>Token codes are sent by email and will be sent to the email address registered on your tesco.com account.</li>
                      <li>Unused, expired and redeemed token codes cannot be refunded, exchanged or returned. This does not affect your statutory rights. </li>
